name: In the eye of the beholder
description:
In the eye of the beholder, there are stones that tremble. Her shadow fears that shadow and her lips are drugs, and her shadow fears that mouth. Her shadow fears that shadow and her lips are skies and her hue is dusk.
She fears that twin that sleeps in her shadow, and that in her sleep she secretly longs for that same night threesome that her shadow despairs.
